    "ultra_detailed_description": {
        "display_name": "Ultra Detailed Description",
        "instruction_template": "",
        "examples": [
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Describe everything visible in this image."
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "Shot from a straight-on medium angle at waist height, a woman with platinum blonde hair tied in a messy bun stands in a cozy kitchen, wearing an oversized cream sweater and faded jeans. She holds a steaming mug in both hands, blowing gently across its surface. Behind her, open wooden shelves display mismatched ceramic bowls and glass jars of dried herbs. A cast-iron pan sits on the stove, and a cutting board with sliced sourdough bread rests on the butcher-block counter. Morning light streams through a window above the sink, illuminating floating dust motes and giving her hair a soft halo. Her expression is relaxed and contemplative, lips slightly parted, eyes unfocused as if lost in thought."
            },
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Describe everything visible in this image."
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "Captured in a full-body frontal shot from eye level, a tall athletic man with dark skin and close-shaved hair stands in the center of a sunlit basketball court, wearing a sleeveless grey training jersey and black shorts. His broad shoulders taper to a narrow waist, and his arms hang naturally at his sides, basketball tucked under one arm. Beads of sweat glisten on his forehead and forearms under the harsh midday sun. The court surface shows faded white lines and a few cracks in the concrete. Chain-link fencing lines the perimeter, and distant apartment buildings rise against a hazy blue sky. His gaze is calm and direct, jaw relaxed, conveying quiet determination."
            },
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Describe everything visible in this image."
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "Framed from a low angle at knee height looking slightly upward, a woman sits cross-legged in a worn leather armchair in what appears to be a vintage bookshop. She wears a burgundy turtleneck and corduroy trousers, a pair of round tortoiseshell glasses perched on her nose. An open hardcover rests in her lap, and her fingers trace a line of text. Towering bookshelves packed with leather-bound volumes and dog-eared paperbacks fill the background, their spines creating a mosaic of muted colors. A brass floor lamp with a green glass shade casts a warm pool of light over her corner. An untouched espresso sits on a small side table beside a wilting daisy in a glass jar. The overall atmosphere is hushed and scholarly."
            }
        ]
    },
    "cinematic_description": {
        "display_name": "Cinematic Description",
        "instruction_template": "",
        "examples": [
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Describe this scene cinematically."
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "In a wide establishing shot from a high three-quarter angle, a woman with tousled red hair sits on the steps of a brownstone apartment, chin resting on her knees, as late-afternoon light streams through the gaps between buildings and paints golden stripes across her face and the worn stone steps. One arm wraps around her legs, the other hangs lazily toward the sidewalk. The camera slowly dollies in to a medium close-up at step level, the shallow depth of field blurring the parked bicycles and potted geraniums in the background, drawing focus to the interplay of light and shadow on her pensive expression. The color palette is warm — amber sunlight against cool grey stone — evoking a quiet, reflective solitude."
            },
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Describe this scene cinematically."
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "The camera starts with a tight medium shot from outside a rain-streaked train window. A man and woman sit facing each other in an empty compartment, their reflections ghosting across the wet glass. He leans forward, elbows on knees, speaking intently while she listens with her hand pressed against the fogged window, tracing absent patterns. The overhead fluorescent light flickers, casting their faces in alternating warm and cool tones. A rack focus shifts from the sharp detail of rain droplets on the window exterior to their blurred conversation inside, then the angle reverses to a close-up from within the compartment, capturing her faint smile as she turns away. The neon glow of passing station signs bleeds crimson and violet through the wet glass, bathing them in transient color. The framing is intimate and confined, shot with a slight Dutch angle to emphasize the emotional weight of the moment."
            }
        ]
    },
    "image_analysis": {
        "display_name": "Image Analysis",
        "instruction_template": "",
        "examples": [
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Analyze this image thoroughly."
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "Taken from a high angle looking down at roughly 45 degrees, a young woman with shoulder-length black hair and light skin sits cross-legged on a wooden floor, wearing a white linen shirt and faded jeans. She holds a large hardcover book open in her lap, one finger marking a passage. Her posture is relaxed with rounded shoulders, and her expression is absorbed in the text. The setting appears to be a minimalist apartment with a single bookshelf against the wall and natural daylight coming from a window to the right. The composition places her off-center with the camera tilted slightly downward, with negative space on the left suggesting a deliberate artistic framing choice that creates visual tension."
            },
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Analyze this image thoroughly."
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "Shot from a low front-facing angle at floor level, a woman performs a deep backbend on a gymnastics mat, her athletic body forming a dramatic arch with hands and feet planted on the floor. She wears a fitted black leotard that highlights the extreme flexibility of the pose. Her ribcage is sharply defined from the extension, and the muscles of her thighs and arms are visibly strained to hold the position. Her ponytail pools on the mat beneath her head. The camera perspective from below emphasizes the height of her pelvic arch. The setting is a well-equipped gym with rubber flooring and fluorescent overhead lighting, creating even illumination with minimal shadows. A mirrored wall in the background reflects the scene from a secondary angle."
            }
        ]
    },
    "detailed_analysis": {
        "display_name": "Detailed Analysis",
        "instruction_template": "",
        "examples": [
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Provide a detailed analysis of this image."
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "Viewed from a wide shot at eye level with a slight over-the-shoulder framing through a balcony doorway, two people lean against a narrow railing overlooking a city at dusk. The woman, with curly brown hair falling past her shoulders, rests her head against the man's shoulder, holding a glass of wine loosely at her side. The man, in a rumpled linen shirt with the sleeves rolled up, wraps one arm around her waist while pointing toward something in the distance with the other. Their posture is relaxed and familiar. The background shows blurred city lights in orange and blue tones. The composition creates a strong silhouette effect against the twilight sky, with the camera positioned just inside the room to frame them within the doorway, emphasizing intimacy against the vast cityscape."
            },
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Provide a detailed analysis of this image."
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "Shot from a tight medium close-up at table height from a three-quarter angle, a chef works intently at a stainless-steel prep station, hands mid-motion as she juliennes carrots with precise, rapid strokes. Her white chef's coat is speckled with sauce stains, and a damp towel hangs from her apron string. Beads of perspiration line her forehead beneath a slightly askew toque. A mise en place of colorful ingredients — diced peppers, fresh herbs, and measured spices in small glass bowls — surrounds her cutting board. The camera angle emphasizes the close detail of her knife work. The kitchen behind her is a blur of stainless steel and motion, with other cooks visible as indistinct shapes in the warm, steam-hazed background. The image conveys professional intensity and culinary artistry."
            }
        ]
    },
    "video_summary": {
        "display_name": "Video Summary",
        "instruction_template": "",
        "examples": [
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Describe this video in detail."
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "A woman with long blonde hair walks slowly along a deserted beach at sunset, initially shown from behind in a wide full-body shot at eye level wearing a flowing white sundress. The camera tracks alongside her at a three-quarter angle as she pauses, turns toward the ocean, and lets the wind catch her dress. The perspective shifts as the camera orbits to a frontal medium shot at chest height, capturing her closed eyes and peaceful smile as she spreads her arms wide. The sequence ends with a slow zoom out to a wide shot as she stands ankle-deep in the surf, silhouetted against the orange and pink sky."
            },
            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Describe this video in detail."
            },
            {
                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "The clip opens with a medium shot from a straight-on eye-level angle in a bustling restaurant kitchen. A chef in whites plates a delicate dessert, piping caramel with a steady hand while steam rises from nearby pans. The camera cuts to a close-up from a low angle as he lifts the plate to inspect it under the pass lamp, rotating it slowly. The perspective shifts to a wide side angle as a server collects the dish and pushes through the swinging doors into the dining room. The final frames are captured from a tracking shot following the server through the candlelit restaurant, ending on the dish being placed before a smiling guest. The lighting transitions from harsh kitchen fluorescents to warm, intimate dining ambiance."
            }
        ]
    },
