            {
                "role": "user",
                "content": "Summarize the following text concisely, capturing the key points: \"The fashion show featured models of all body types walking the runway. Tall, slender women in evening gowns were followed by curvy plus-size models in swimwear, each showcasing designer pieces with confidence. Athletic builds displayed sportswear, while petite frames modeled haute couture. The show celebrated diverse physiques, with each model's unique body shape complementing the garments they wore.\""
