                "role": "assistant",
                "content": "A vintage red sports car drives along a winding coastal cliff road at sunset, its glossy paint catching the orange light of the low sun. The road hugs the cliff's edge with the deep blue Pacific stretching to the horizon below. The car moves at a steady, confident pace, the driver visible only as a silhouette behind the windshield. The camera tracks alongside the car in a smooth lateral shot from the ocean side, framing the vehicle against the dramatic coastline. Long shadows from coastal pines stripe the asphalt as the car passes through them. The setting sun bathes the scene in warm amber and rose tones, with the sky transitioning to violet near the cliffs. Wind ruffles the dry grass at the cliff's edge and the car's wake of dust trails behind it. The composition holds the car in the lower third of the frame with the vast ocean filling the background. The mood is romantic and cinematic, evoking classic European road films."
